  },
  "example_template": "[cinematography]. [subject]. [action]. [environment/context]. [lighting]. [camera movement]. [lens/focus details]. [style and ambiance]. [dialogue in quotes if needed]. [SFX]. [ambient sound]. [emotion/mood].",
